image.altText: Scott Morrison high vis

props.synopsis: The former prime minister Scott Morrison was not shy in his dealings with foreign leaders, adversaries or the press gallery. But he has ended his political career quietly, with a simple post on Facebook.

title.children: 'Miracle' man Scott Morrison calls time on political career, new job beckons in US

image.altText: A man with dark, short hair and a serious expression speaks in front of SA government backdrop.

props.synopsis: The government and opposition want to see mandatory life imprisonment and lifetime electronic monitoring for repeat child sex offenders, but lawyers say they're concerned the proposition could have unintended consequences.

title.children: 'Lock them away and throw out the key': SA to fast track tougher laws for child sex offenders

image.altText: Generic photo of people swimming in the ocean at an Adelaide beach on a hot day.

props.synopsis: Parts of South Australia's Eyre Peninsula and far north reached temperatures above 47 degrees on Tuesday, as a cool change is forecast to sweep through the state overnight.

title.children: Adelaide swelters through warmest day in nearly three years as cool changes sweeps through SA

image.altText: A boat docking with people waiting

image.altText: A man smiling at the camera while screwing something into a wall.

image.altText: Jim Chalmers in the foreground in focus, with Anthony Albanese in the background out of focus, from the right hand side

props.synopsis: Ahead of Labor's cost-of-living caucus, the crosshairs have again settled on the stage 3 tax cuts that are months away from handing more than $20 billion a year from the government back to (mainly) higher income earners.

image.altText: Woman wearing a black top smiling for a portrait.

image.altText: Tasmanian Police Officer Paul Reynolds at a press conference.

image.altText: A row of blue and white flowers and photographs are laid out above a Victoria Police marble floor.

image.altText: Glenn Maxwell

image.altText: A woman sitting in a car.

image.altText: Woman with a striped jumper works on a laptop while holding a baby at a desk in her home.

image.altText: A crowd of people gathered outside a temple
